title: Fixed scaling issues to allow game to be run at any resolution including tablets.
message: Fixed scaling issues to allow game to be run at any resolution including tablets.

title: Added Log class for logging purposes. It allows you to turn on and off debug…
message: Added Log class for logging purposes. It allows you to turn on and off debug mode. Make sure to turn it off before building release version. Removed unused sprites and variables used for old interface.

title: Added game instructions. Added ball invincibility. Changed the score label in…
message: Added game instructions. Added ball invincibility. Changed the score label in game to use new scene2d interface. Changed how game saves. Changed app icon.  Removed all unused classes.

title: Remade the entire user interface using the Scene2D library. As a result, added…
message: Remade the entire user interface using the Scene2D library. As a result, added UI skins and multiple new classes. A few depreciated and unused methods and classes now exist which will need to be cleaned up in the future.

title: Refactored all the level generation code to a new class. Added environment…
message: Refactored all the level generation code to a new class. Added environment sprites. Cleaned up some code here and there.
